rows.label: qev025905_MSG0001
rows.name:
Humans are mere tools, yet you have the audacity to
turn upon your master? Such cheek![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0002
rows.name:
Tools are meant to serve their role in eager submission.
Tools are meant to act like our dear Fraisie.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0003
rows.name:
But ours is a benevolent god, and there is still time for
you to repent and accept her command. Now prove
your faith, kill the Ma-non, and sow chaos in New LA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_SEL0011
rows.name: Defy the orders of her god.

rows.label: qev025905_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask your opponent to reveal its true identity.

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0004
rows.name: Fool! I see now why the Ganglion despise your ilk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0005
rows.name:
I am an avatar of god, in the purest sense! One of a
host of daughters to Mother Fortun, our flesh the
incarnation of her glorious will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0006
rows.name:
...But enough. You shall live only long enough
to regret challenging TW772: Trinnâ€”bearer
of the Tower's name![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025905_MSG0007
rows.name:
Bear witness, Mother! I shall lay bare all the power
and cruelty within me![ST:wait ]
